  "prompt": "Which are the best indian restaurants?",
  "response": "The best Indian restaurants can vary based on location, personal taste, and what specific dishes you enjoy. However, here are some highly regarded Indian restaurants from various parts of the world:\n\n### United States\n1. **Dishoom** (London, UK) - While it's not in the U.S., Dishoom offers a unique Bombay caf\u00e9 experience.\n2. **Minar Indian Cuisine** (Katy, Texas) - Known for its authentic North Indian flavors.\n3. **Chola** (New York City) - Celebrated for its South Indian dishes and upscale ambiance.\n4. **Bombay Brasserie** (London, UK) - Offers modern Indian cuisine with a twist.\n\n### United Kingdom\n1. **Gymkhana** (London) - Michelin-starred Indian restaurant with a focus on colonial Indian cuisine.\n2. **Tamarind** (London) - Known for its sophisticated dishes and elegant setting.\n3. **Dishoom** (Multiple Locations) - Offers a unique caf\u00e9 experience inspired by the Irani caf\u00e9s of Bombay.\n\n### Canada\n1. **Sula Indian Restaurant** (Toronto) - Known for its innovative approach to traditional dishes.\n2. **Bukhara** (Ottawa) - Celebrated for its North Indian recipes and ambiance.\n\n### Australia\n1. **Spice Temple** (Sydney) - Offers a modern interpretation of Chinese-Indian cuisine.\n2. **Delhi Street** (Melbourne) - Known for its authentic Indian street food.\n\n### India\n1. **Bukhara** (New Delhi) - Iconic for its tandoori cooking and rustic charm.\n2. **Karavalli** (Bengaluru) - Celebrates coastal Indian cuisine with traditional recipes.\n3. **Indian Accent** (New Delhi) - A Michelin-starred restaurant known for its contemporary approach to Indian flavors.\n\n### Middle East\n1. **Zafaran** (Dubai) - Offers a blend of traditional and modern Indian dishes.\n2. **Bukhara** (Dubai) - Another branch of the famous New Delhi restaurant known for its robust flavors.\n\nThese recommendations provide a blend of both casual and fine dining experiences, each showcasing the richness of Indian cuisine. It\u2019s always a good idea to check local reviews and menus to find the perfect fit for your tastes!",
